{"tid":1292393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再忍，發起搜捕懷疑冒警人士活動","createTime":"2019-07-07T09:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:56:39.000Z","uid":99805,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"faeabe452bb7aaaf59d1daf4894599009ebc46ba","tid":1292393,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"根據警察通例<br />\n所有便衣警員行使警權時必需出示委任證<br />\n既然街上有咁多出示唔到委任證既人自稱警察<br />\n作為守法既公民，我地亦有責任要防止罪案發生<br />\n<br />\n我認為個做法係大家可以印下面既警例<br />\n首先出示警例比懷疑冒警者<br />\n如果對方堅持唔出示證件<br />\n<br />\n就琴日屯門一事，肯企出黎既人<br />\n一定足夠圍住懷疑冒警人士<br />\n假如對方要走，<br />\n大家應該立即手拖手圍住呢班人並打999救助<br />\n<br />\n如對方行使武力更加唔可以比佢地走<br />\n一定要在場警察拘捕未有出視委任證又行使不合法武力既人，記住，未出示委任證即係未能證明佢係警察<br />\n<br />\n支持守法，行使警權一定要出示委任證<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQ2VmvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQ2VmvR.png&h=ab27356f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb128006665a6b7f8b34a6cfe524450c30bdedcf","tid":1292393,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a1f907b363601e79274a0ff260ec98b7af0b44b","tid":1292393,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec2f58946c071ae00084b668e8a743fc6df10797","tid":1292393,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"77bbb1ccfcc2573cf8202f18692f65f5332b71c8","tid":1292393,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"4a 呢條萬能 key<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abede87946121976ea1015f863f40aebfa55787f","tid":1292393,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77bbb1ccfcc2573cf8202f18692f65f5332b71c8","tid":1292393,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"4a 呢條萬能 key<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c